<!-- <UL>
<H2>Issue: Recursive PROPFIND,Remove INDEX</H2>
</UL></P>
<P><UL>
<LI><H2>Problem: 
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Set of properties returned by INDEX is arbitrary
<LI>Results in a large amount of data transfer for large collections.
</UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Proposed Solution: 
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Make PROPFIND work recursively, allowing retrieval of client-specified sets of properties. 
<LI>This makes PROPFIND, in essence, a customizable INDEX.  
<LI>Remove the INDEX method since it is now redundant.
</UL></UL></P>
